Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:26.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:28.40,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.72,0:02:32.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel{-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:41.80,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have your wallet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:42.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:43.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Identification?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.52,0:02:44.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.07,0:02:44.76,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Handkerchief?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:45.40,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:46.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Tissue?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.13,0:02:46.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:47.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Map?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:47.97,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:48.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Compass?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:49.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:50.45,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Instant food?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.45,0:02:50.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:51.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:52.60,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:53.61,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:54.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:55.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Grenades?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:56.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:03:00.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a joke, Kana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:03.61,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared me, jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.61,0:03:06.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were thinking calmly, you would've caught on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.24,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a bully, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:14.75,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been getting along well lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:19.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio is just like a worried mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:23.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this is today's list.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.48,0:03:29.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. Today's mission is for you to go downtown and purchase the supplies on that list.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:30.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:31.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.63,0:03:34.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, drive safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:35.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:40.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Proceeding to depart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:45.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:48.16,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We're having pot-au-feu for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:50.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just like a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:50.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H585858&}Don't take any detours, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.66,0:04:00.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our first time going into town together, isn't it Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:00.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:02.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But then again,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:06.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,it's like the first time ever going into town for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:10.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:13.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:19.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This was completely different during the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:23.19,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's such a calm and quiet town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:34.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow-ow-ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:37.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,First was Nue, a roof decoration particular to Trois.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:40.47,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Its purpose is to ward off evil spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:41.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:43.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Next was the fountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:46.73,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's modeled after the Twelfth Archduke of Helvetia,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:48.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira Arcadia the Second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:54.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:57.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, from earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:57.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:04:59.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I drove safely, as I was told.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:03.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thank you! Now I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:05.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You know a lot, don't you Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:11.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:14.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You coming in or not? Decide already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You're messing with business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:22.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the granny from the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:23.97,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's "miss".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:26.92,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be pushy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:30.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You're as stiff as usual, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:32.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at least call me Naomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:35.19,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Naomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:49.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So the next shipment is next month?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:50.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:53.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.34,0:05:56.16,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:02.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all so unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:03.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're soldiers{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:04.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.08,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:07.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:13.16,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You had your eye on it the first time you came here, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:14.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:22.61,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... M-May I touch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:23.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:35.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,A-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:44.61,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a fish, isn't it? What's it called?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:46.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:47.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:49.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:50.22,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a dolphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:53.70,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more closely related to humans than fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:57.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a marine mammal back when the seas still had life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:59.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea? It lived in the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:06:59.99,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:10.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That old man really does have skill, making stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.54,0:07:14.45,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,He might not look it, but he's a romanticist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:17.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the person who made it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.11,0:07:19.75,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a big factory on the outskirts of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:22.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,All of our glassware comes from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.45,0:07:27.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see where they made this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:28.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:28.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:31.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going there afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:40.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so that glass factory makes a part used in the Takemikazuchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:45.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Naomi is also collecting parts from the old era.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:49.96,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you really are awesome, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:52.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You can fix that complex machine in a jiffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:53.89,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,"Jiffy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:08:00.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I have trouble just trying to remember all the trumpet calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.72,0:08:04.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not... a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:09.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... machines never betray me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:12.74,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:13.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:16.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The change is 2,750,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really that much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:22.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Incorrect. It's 2 yen and 75 sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:25.80,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Cold as usual, aren't you, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:28.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Your change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:30.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:33.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been doing the morning calls recently, missy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:34.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:37.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm still bad at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:38.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:43.29,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I like it. How do I put it...  It's sure to wake me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:49.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Stare.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:56.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing! I just need to get better soon so I don't bother the townspeople...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:06.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair, Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:09.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, I{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:10.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H585858&}Catch me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:13.26,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:14.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm sor{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:18.26,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah, you ran into someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:20.08,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.61,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You girls are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:25.74,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You're from the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:25.74,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H585858&}The airhead girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:29.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:31.92,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're well again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:45.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.43,0:09:51.44,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya! They had nothing to do with your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:52.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:54.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate {\i1}all{\i0} soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:56.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get out of here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:10:00.81,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And your crappy bugle irritates me every morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:03.89,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:06.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:07.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That was uncalled-for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:09.19,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:12.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a wartime orphan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:15.24,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, he sees all militaries the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:18.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:19.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:23.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that we are soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:27.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:02.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:05.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}We're soldiers, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:10.16,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}I took the Parador Oath when I enlisted,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:11.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}and I thought I understood it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.18,0:11:16.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what am I talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:18.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something I knew from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:20.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point hesitating about it now, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:28.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I just need to improve in case something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.63,0:11:31.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will be in trouble if there are no trumpet calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:32.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We're close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.54,0:11:38.64,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the glass factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:39.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:41.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it amazing, Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:44.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a building that large before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is also a failure, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:08.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe optical aberrations?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:11.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure the refraction is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:21.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm Sorami Kanata, the new recruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.85,0:12:23.45,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:24.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:31.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how's the timing when the errors occur?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:33.32,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The seek-times don't deviate much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:37.64,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Closed distortion within the peripherals has decreased somewhat from the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:37.64,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H585858&}Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:43.45,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,When the boss talks about work, he thinks of nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:46.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But old man Carl is truly awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:51.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of five people in this country who hold the title of Meister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:52.64,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a brilliant artisan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:58.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Once, he won a national competition and got to present his work to the Archduke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:03.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria, if you have time to talk, move your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:04.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.19,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:10.45,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, I can't take pride in being called a "Meister",
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:13.19,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,since I can't even get these things to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:15.76,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.76,0:13:18.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The optical sensor lens for the Takemikazuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:20.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:26.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,To repair the Takemikazuchi, I need two identical lenses. So I ordered a reproduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:28.74,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, they don't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they're so beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:34.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Other than silicon dioxide as its primary element,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:38.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,a lens also needs to be infused with additional sodium oxide and magnesium oxide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:41.75,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is to correct chromatic and peripheral aberrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:44.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it removes distortion in the captured image.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:47.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, we don't know the ratios.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:53.64,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The technology of the past era practically works like magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:14:03.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought glass was just pretty to look at, but it's quite complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:09.90,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Seize has high-quality silica deposits,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:13.76,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,several small factories were built to produce glassware.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:17.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This was originally one of those small factories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:21.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, as the war progressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:24.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,demand for glassware with military application increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:28.47,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This factory prospered thanks to the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:43.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:44.98,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I love machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:46.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:50.29,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, there are times when machines hurt people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:55.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the Takemikazuchi has killed several people in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:03.92,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think machines that have killed people are scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:07.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:10.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:16.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I fear the people using those machines more than the machines themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:22.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this trumpet for example, you know how it sounds when I play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:25.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But when Rio plays it, it sounds so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:27.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure tanks are the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:36.75,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Rio let me hear the Takemikazuchi's song the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:39.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It could sing such a beautiful song.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:56.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the Takemikazuchi is a nice tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:06.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, let's listen to it next{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:14.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:17.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Let her sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:23.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She must've pulled an all-nighter again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:28.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She works very hard to fix the Takemikazuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:29.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:32.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is a real worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:38.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I wouldn't have taken the task of making this troublesome part.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:40.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Put this on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:44.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.18,0:16:48.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you two stopped by the Windmill, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:50.45,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Naomi doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:52.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:56.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She said the Boss is a wonderful romanticist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:58.19,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:17:00.16,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:01.90,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:04.24,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back to work already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:06.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, he got mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:08.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:19.97,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But is the past technology really that awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:21.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:25.22,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the Boss always says this:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:33.03,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,"No matter how awesome it is, it was made by a human. There's no way we can't do the same!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:35.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:36.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:38.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I want to say yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:45.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:50.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, your performance is very different from Rio's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:54.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always wondering how I can play just like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:58.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm practicing so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.50,0:18:01.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Even my lips are swollen because of it, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:05.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:09.73,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't produce the same sound as her no matter how much I try.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:13.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I really have no talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:14.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Missy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:15.03,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:19.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,"Talent" is the worst excuse for someone who has given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:20.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:24.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not know much about trumpets,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:30.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,but newbies do make plenty of mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:34.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Missy, aren't you trying to too hard to produce the sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:07.75,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm trying to shape it like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:11.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,the glass is the one that wanted to take this shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:22.67,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, old man Carl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:56.08,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the notes resound by themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:44.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:50.48,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's as if the sun has just come up for that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:53.29,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is a worker too, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:54.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:56.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:08.74,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the glass changes slightly depending on amount and type of impurity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:12.08,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Though our normal ears may not catch the difference,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:15.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,one with outstanding hearing should be able to tell them apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:21.84,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I will have Kanata check these samples and determine which comes closest in sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.90,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do that, then maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:28.26,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, listen to the voices of these samples, missy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:29.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.13,0:21:53.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel has changed a lot since she joined, hasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:54.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.13,0:21:54.99,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:19.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it! You did it, Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:25.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.63,0:22:35.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time seeing Noel smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.01,0:24:19.98,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Next episode: Mountain Climbing - The End of the World
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.85,0:00:18.24,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}The radiance of this sky will carry to your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.84,0:00:28.55,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}The melody you dreamed of is like serenity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:33.54,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}For your hands the dream is still far away, but
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:38.54,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}remember the voice so gentle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:51.23,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}when someone sang the chord of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:01:00.70,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}The sound of the skies echoes high over all sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.70,0:01:11.34,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}Everything reflected in your eyes is the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:20.68,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}Not even the shedding of of tears can stop you here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.68,0:01:33.24,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}We're playing tomorrow in the light that rains without end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.43,0:22:51.22,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Pile up the feelings of love and friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.22,0:22:54.31,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Performing is also important
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.70,0:23:12.31,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I cried happily
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.45,0:23:18.26,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I laughed eagerly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.72,0:23:27.57,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}But all of them make me alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.57,0:23:31.71,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Let's walk slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.71,0:23:33.56,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Everybody singing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.56,0:23:37.66,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Tell me why we dance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.66,0:23:38.93,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}you just my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.93,0:23:45.09,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Even if love and friendship change over time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.09,0:23:50.55,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I want them to echo forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.09,0:23:56.87,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Speaking endless words touched by love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.87,0:24:03.01,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.03,0:24:07.64,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I can hear our harmony
